<HEADLINE>
FT  07 JAN 94 / World News in Brief: Eastern German population to fall
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The population of eastern Germany will fall by 20 per cent by 2010 because
of migration to the prosperous west and a declining birth rate, researchers
at Humboldt University, Berlin, said.
