FT  07 JAN 94 / UK Company News: Exports help Druck rise to Pounds 2m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Increased exports helped raise pre-tax profits at Druck Holdings, the
manufacturer of electronic pressure measuring devices, by 19 per cent from
